            Our Program
          Heading link



 
Copy link



            100% online university classes for college credit in the natural sciences, humanities and social sciences as well as courses in business, computer science, engineering and education. All classes are taught by UIC faculty in 8-week or 16-week sessions. Courses are offered during fall, spring, and summer terms and students receive a UIC transcript. Spring classes start January 9.
          






